<item>
            <title>[LU-6614] strip extra / from $DIR in sanity.sh</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6614</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We hit that several tests fail when $DIR has extra &quot;/&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity test 226a: call path2fid and fid2path on files of all type == 06:27:59 (1394692079)
 sanity test_226a: @@@@@@ FAIL: fid2path returned /mnt/fs1/d0.sanity/d226/fifo, expected /mnt/fs1//d0.sanity/d226/fifo

== sanity test 162: path lookup sanity == 05:17:42 (1394687862)
fid 0x200001be7:0x59:0x0 resolves to path d0.sanity/d162/d2/f.sanity.162 (expected d0.sanity/d162/d2/f.sanity.162)
fid 0x200001be7:0x66:0x0 resolves to path d0.sanity/d162/d2/p/q/r/slink (expected d0.sanity/d162/d2/p/q/r/slink)
fid 0x200001be7:0x67:0x0 resolves to path d0.sanity/d162/d2/p/q/r/slink.wrong (expected d0.sanity/d162/d2/p/q/r/slink.wrong)
fid 0x200001be7:0x59:0x0 resolves to path d0.sanity/d162/d2/a/b/c/new_file (expected d0.sanity/d162/d2/a/b/c/new_file)
 sanity test_162: @@@@@@ FAIL: path looked up &quot;/mnt/fs1/d0.sanity/d162/d2/p/q/r/hlink&quot; instead of &quot;/mnt/fs1//d0.sanity/d162/d2/p/q/r/hlink&quot; 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

</description>
